{"data": [{"id": "4743748", "title": "Google's Waymo Continues To Surge Ahead Of Tesla", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158937921/image_2158937921.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Waymo Jaguar driverless car drives on urban street in San Francisco\" data-id=\"2158937921\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158937921/image_2158937921.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158937921/image_2158937921.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158937921/image_2158937921.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158937921/image_2158937921.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158937921/image_2158937921.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158937921/image_2158937921.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158937921/image_2158937921.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158937921/image_2158937921.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Michael Vi/iStock Editorial via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Google\u2019s (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/GOOG\" title=\"Alphabet Inc.\">GOOG</a></span>) Waymo is finally showing a strong runway as it expands in new regions and increases its cash pile. Recently, Waymo announced a massive $5.6 billion funding round. It is already having an impact on</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158937921/image_2158937921.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743748-googles-waymo-continues-to-surge-ahead-of-tesla", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 08:09:43"}, {"id": "4740942", "title": "Politics And The Markets 12/12/24", "description": "<p><span>This is the forum for daily political discussion on Seeking Alpha. A new version is published every market day.</span></p> <p>Please don't leave political comments on other articles or posts on the site.</p> <p>The comments below are not regulated with the same rigor as the rest of the site, and this is an <strong>'enter at your own risk' </strong>area as discussion can get very heated. If you can't stand the heat... you know what they say...</p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span>More on Today's Markets:</span></b></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span></span></b></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>Moderation Guidelines:</b></p> <p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><b><span></span></b>We remove comments under the following categories:</p> <ul> <li>Personal attacks on another user account</li> <li>Anti-Vaxxer or covid related misinformation</li> <li>Stereotyping, prejudiced or racist language about individuals or the topic under discussion.</li> <li>Inciting violence messages, encouraging hate groups and political violence.</li> </ul> <p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Regardless of which side of the political divide you find yourself, please be courteous and don't direct abuse at other users.</p> <p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">For any issue with regards to comments please email us at : moderation@seekingalpha.com.</p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span>Seeking Alpha's Disclosure:</span></b><span> Past performance is no guarantee of future results. No recommendation or advice is being given as to whether any investment is suitable for a particular investor. Any views or opinions expressed above may not reflect those of Seeking Alpha as a whole. Seeking Alpha is not a licensed securities dealer, broker or US investment adviser or investment bank. Our analysts are third party authors that include both professional investors and individual investors who may not be licensed or certified by any institute or regulatory body.</span></p> <p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"> </p> <div class=\"before_last_paragraph-piano-placeholder\"></div> <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span></span></b></p> <div class=\"sa-art article-width paywall-full-content\" id=\"a-body\"><span class=\"content-end p p1\"></span></div>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4740942-politics-and-the-markets-121224", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 08:00:00"}, {"id": "4743742", "title": "CGDV: Light On Dividends But An Excellent Mix Of Growth And Value", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/826530516/image_826530516.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Focus on fundamentals\" data-id=\"826530516\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1017px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/826530516/image_826530516.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/826530516/image_826530516.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/826530516/image_826530516.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/826530516/image_826530516.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/826530516/image_826530516.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/826530516/image_826530516.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/826530516/image_826530516.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/826530516/image_826530516.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">tang90246</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Investment Thesis</h2> <p>I <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4678621-cgdv-top-performing-dividend-etf-with-excellent-earnings-growth-potential\">last reviewed</a> the Capital Group Dividend Value ETF (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSEARCA:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CGDV\" title=\"Capital Group Dividend Value ETF\">CGDV</a></span>) on March 15, 2024, when I reiterated my \"buy\" rating due to its solid combination of growth and value. Since my <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4636449-cgdv-actively-managed-dividend-etf-beating-the-market\">initial coverage</a></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/826530516/image_826530516.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743742-cgdv-light-on-dividends-but-an-excellent-mix-of-growth-and-value", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 07:52:00"}, {"id": "4743744", "title": "Crocs' Valuation Can Be Capitalized On In The Near Term", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173831350/image_173831350.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Sand &amp; sandals\" data-id=\"173831350\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173831350/image_173831350.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173831350/image_173831350.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173831350/image_173831350.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173831350/image_173831350.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173831350/image_173831350.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173831350/image_173831350.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173831350/image_173831350.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173831350/image_173831350.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">cunfek/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Crocs (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CROX\" title=\"Crocs, Inc.\">CROX</a></span>) is a unique footwear company with a distinct brand and potential for international growth. However, given slower growth rates after a large increase in brand awareness from the pandemic, the company isn't a growth investment</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173831350/image_173831350.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743744-crocs-stock-valuation-can-be-capitalized-on-in-near-term", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 07:48:02"}, {"id": "4743741", "title": "Tracking Baker Brothers Portfolio - Q3 2024 Update", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1160060870/image_1160060870.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Pharmaceuticals Medical Stock Market Industry Sector Wall Street Buildings 3d Illustration\" data-id=\"1160060870\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5000px\" height=\"3000px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1160060870/image_1160060870.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1160060870/image_1160060870.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1160060870/image_1160060870.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1160060870/image_1160060870.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1160060870/image_1160060870.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1160060870/image_1160060870.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1160060870/image_1160060870.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1160060870/image_1160060870.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">iQoncept</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>This article is part of a series that provides an ongoing analysis of the changes made to Baker Brothers\u2019 13F stock portfolio on a quarterly basis. It is based on Baker Brothers\u2019 regulatory <a href=\"https://www.sec.gov/Archives/edgar/data/1263508/000110465924118899/0001104659-24-118899-index.htm\" rel=\"nofollow\">13F Form</a> filed on 11/14/2024. The</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1160060870/image_1160060870.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743741-tracking-baker-brothers-portfolio-q3-2024-update", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 07:38:23"}, {"id": "4743750", "title": "CPI Bullish For Long-Term Inflation Outlook", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733234018/image_1733234018.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"CPI, consumer price index concept. Wooden block with the words CPI on coins stack. Goods price inflation and inflation rising. Impact on economic growth with relate icon.\" data-id=\"1733234018\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733234018/image_1733234018.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733234018/image_1733234018.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733234018/image_1733234018.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733234018/image_1733234018.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733234018/image_1733234018.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733234018/image_1733234018.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733234018/image_1733234018.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733234018/image_1733234018.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Boy Wirat</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>CPI printed in-line at .3 on core and headline. Importantly, rent and owners' equivalent rent finally declined to .2 for the month. Other volatile components such as new and used cars, lodging and airline fares were elevated.</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733234018/image_1733234018.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743750-cpi-bullish-for-long-term-inflation-outlook", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 07:20:00"}, {"id": "4743738", "title": "Sun Hung Kai Properties: A Solid Bet On Recovery In Hong Kong And China", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1267068394/image_1267068394.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Drone view of Hong Kong city\" data-id=\"1267068394\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1023px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1267068394/image_1267068394.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1267068394/image_1267068394.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1267068394/image_1267068394.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1267068394/image_1267068394.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1267068394/image_1267068394.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1267068394/image_1267068394.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1267068394/image_1267068394.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1267068394/image_1267068394.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">CHUNYIP WONG/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Investment Thesis</h2> <p><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/author/tudor-invest-holdings/analysis?ticker=SUHJY\">We have covered</a> Sun Hung Kai Properties (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SUHJY\" title=\"Sun Hung Kai Properties Limited\" target=\"_blank\">OTCPK:SUHJY</a>) since 2022, and maintained a bullish view about the stock, despite the tumultuous times that Hong Kong has been going through.</p> <p>Tourism to the city</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1267068394/image_1267068394.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743738-sun-hung-kai-properties-stock-solid-bet-recovery-hong-kong-china", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 07:07:15"}, {"id": "4743737", "title": "Amazon: Why I Am Aggressively Accumulating At All-Time Highs", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1252468735/image_1252468735.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Amazon fulfillment center building in Las Vegas\" data-id=\"1252468735\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"8256px\" height=\"5504px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1252468735/image_1252468735.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1252468735/image_1252468735.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1252468735/image_1252468735.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1252468735/image_1252468735.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1252468735/image_1252468735.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1252468735/image_1252468735.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1252468735/image_1252468735.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1252468735/image_1252468735.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-wid